# Backend
## Environments
/backend/.venv/
/backend/venv/
/backend/env/

## Environment Variables (Secrets!)
/backend/.env

## Python Cache
/backend/__pycache__/
/backend/*.pyc

## Mac System Files
/backend/.DS_Store

